{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>HAVE YOU THE CONVICTION TO FIGHT OFF THE UNHOLY SPAWN!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">            <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2526450/extras/convictionaboutimage1.png?t=1731047584\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stuck in the endless darkness of the world, you must ward off a mysterious cult from summoning their god. Explore the outskirts of a mysterious village in the middle of nowhere as you fight your way through hordes of unholy spawn. Uncover the cult's secrets and stop them for good.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Prove your conviction as you play as a jaded, cynical, priest with nothing but burning rage and a desire to decimate the cult!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dark and Dreary Atmosphere \u2013 the world around you is veiled in eternal darkness...watch your step\u2026</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Relentless Campaign \u2013 fight through fifteen levels over the course of three chapters!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Destructive Arsenal \u2013 use a variety of weapons to decimate all that crosses your path, from a humble revolver to cleansing your foes with fiery Molotov's. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Secrets &amp; Extra Content \u2013 discover secret collectables in each level and you\u2019ll be rewarded with extra items such as health, ammo, or access to secret levels!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2526450/extras/convictionaboutimage2.png?t=1731047584\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2526450/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731047584","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2526450/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1731047584","caps